Title: Supermarket Flowers
Description: ['An animated music video of Ed Sheeran’s song ', Supermarket Flowers, ' from his third studio album, "÷(divide)". The video was directed by Yoriko Hoshi, who’s a winner of a prestigious award: Tezuka Osamu Cultural Prize. The video consists of a heartwarming story, featuring Ed Sheeran and his beloved cats, Calippo and Dorito.']
